  "counters": [],
  "npcs": [
    {
      "name": "Dave",
      "x": 5,
      "y": 6,
      "sprite": "Evil",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Dave",
        "portrait": "Evil",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "GAME OVER MAN!",
          "Haha not really. $#@@*** this though. I gave them the best Kubers and somehow they always have excuses for their outages.",
          "Can you find the root cause for me?",
          "No."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "EV003",
      "x": 8,
      "y": 4,
      "sprite": "Nature",
      "sprite_index": 1,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Amy Tobey",
        "portrait": "Amy",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "The Endgame of SRE",
          "Amy Tobey | @renice@hachyderm.io",
          "Assets by VisuStella"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Agi Lecoach",
      "x": 5,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "Actor2",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Agi Lecoach",
        "portrait": "Actor2",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "I work with all the teams and it's unbelievable how different they are!",
          "The brass hangs out in Mahogany Row. They act like they're the adults in the room but they're just people.",
          "Team Inferno usually delivers except most of the time it doesn't work right.",
          "Team Marathon's velocity has been a straight line for 3 quarters straight. That must be world record. They make it look so easy.",
          "Team Disco tries so darn hard but their velocity is all over the place."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Glenn Gary",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 6,
      "sprite": "Actor1",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Glenn Gary",
        "portrait": "Actor1",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "How am I supposed to sell this product when it keeps crashing in front of prospects!?",
          "The Marathon dudes are always taking days off and laid back. Somehow, their product sells itself.",
          "The Disco geeks always deliver, eventually, but they're never on time and releases are rough. They seem so busy it makes no sense.",
          "Inferno insists they're the best because they work so hard and that part seems true. Thing is, their software isn't usable so it's hard to sell."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Frau Barella",
      "x": 9,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "People4",
      "sprite_index": 7,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Frau Barella",
        "portrait": "People4",
        "face_index": 7,
        "lines": [
          "The great style unification of 2021 is the greatest achievement of our career!",
          "Customers still complain about usability. It's like. Our stuff is great, but it doesn't quite come to gether."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Casey",
      "x": 4,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "casey",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Casey",
        "portrait": "casey",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "If you know who I am I don't know why you're surprised to find me here."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Managear Greg",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "Greg",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Managear Greg",
        "portrait": "Greg",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "As the manager, I protect my people from the politics of this place.",
          "My director says I always have to have a plan for every problem so we're kinda stuck. I don't know what to do."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Devo Pestorius",
      "x": 6,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "People1",
      "sprite_index": 5,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Devo Pestorius",
        "portrait": "People1",
        "face_index": 5,
        "lines": [
          "Our CI/CD is amazing, I should know. So why the heck are we so slow!?",
          "I hate how everyone hides behind their counter and expects me to make everything work in the end."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Polly Math",
      "x": 7,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "People1",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Polly Math",
        "portrait": "People1",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "I need to fix this bug then check in the code I started this morning but then BAM! an incident and tests to fix and patch my kernels",
          "Why would you bring up ADHD?"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Cody",
      "x": 8,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "People1",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Cody",
        "portrait": "People1",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "Stories are never ready for us to work on so I spend all my time chasing requirements."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Cary Erguy",
      "x": 4,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "People2",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Cary Erguy",
        "portrait": "People2",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "I talk to the customers so the engineers don't have to.",
          "I'm a people person!"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Tenchi",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "People1",
      "sprite_index": 2,
      "step_anime": false,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Tenchi",
        "portrait": "People1",
        "face_index": 2,
        "lines": [
          "We all love our work but we're having trouble with our velocity.",
          "We recently split up some of the projects to work on more independently, so we could keep up with the incoming requests.",
          "As Poly Math predicted, they just asked for more and more so we're all lonely and it's hard to help each other now."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Pandora",
      "x": 11,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "Actor2",
      "sprite_index": 5,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Pandora",
        "portrait": "Actor2",
        "face_index": 5,
        "lines": [
          "I finally did it! I showed the customer my sweet a dark mode demo and they demanded we build the before they'll talk about a deal.",
          "Our service doesn't really need themes but I knew this prospect would love it."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Cee Eeoh",
      "x": 9,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "People3",
      "sprite_index": 0,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Cee Eeoh",
        "portrait": "People3",
        "face_index": 0,
        "lines": [
          "Pandora opened up a lead for us. The customer loved the dark mode mockup.",
          "I double clicked on that vision and had an epiphany. What if customers could theme the whole site!? Should be easy.",
          "I was so excited I texted my guy on Team Inferno. He dropped everything and started work on it right away."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Vee Peapod",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 7,
      "sprite": "People4",
      "sprite_index": 6,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Vee Peapod",
        "portrait": "People4",
        "face_index": 6,
        "lines": [
          "I heard Cee Eeoh needs a new color wheel in the app so I told Team Disco to get that ready as soon as possible."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Mistress of Scrum",
      "x": 11,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "Monster",
      "sprite_index": 5,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Mistress of Scrum",
        "portrait": "Monster",
        "face_index": 5,
        "lines": [
          "We are forming a tiger team to implement the new Pantone values right away."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Gantt",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 8,
      "sprite": "SF_Monster",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Gantt",
        "portrait": "SF_Monster",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "Why is it so hard for these meatbags to understand our SDLC? They call it Waterscrumfall, whatever that means.",
          "These fools write down stories in messy English. Hah! One thing at a time, that's the way!"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Desi Goner",
      "x": 11,
      "y": 6,
      "sprite": "SF_Actor1",
      "sprite_index": 5,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Desi Goner",
        "portrait": "SF_Actor1",
        "face_index": 5,
        "lines": [
